    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>How about just:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static String intToString(int num, int digits) {\n    String output = Integer.toString(num);\n    while (output.length() &lt; digits) output = \"0\" + output;\n    return output;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
